title: Comedy Nights with Kapil - Imran & Kareena 24th Nov HQ 480p
description:
The episode starts with Kapil cracking jokes on ghosts and devils. Kapil then proceeds to insult his wife and father-in- law. Kapil's Dadi again touches upon the topic of Kapil and his wife not having a child. Later, Imran Khan and Kareena Kapoor join Kapil on the show, to promote their movie - Gori Tere Pyar Mein. Watch the episode and have a hearty laugh.

Renowned, actor-comedian Kapil Sharma makes his debut as a TV show producer with his new show Comedy Nights With Kapil. He will be seen multiple roles of an actor, scriptwriter and producer in his production debut. Already famous for his amazing comic timing and his talent to dig humor out of any situation, he is ready present everyday life in a fresh ad unique way.
